            <h1>Welcome, Music Fan.</h1>
			<br />
            <h4 class="text-secondary">Lets start with this: we <strong class="text-danger">LOVE</strong> music.</h4>
			
			<p>In fact, just like you, we can go into seemingly endless detail about what we love on our favorite records. As streaming has become a larger part of the music industry, we started to find it harder and harder to keep track of all the music in our libraries. We also noticed we were missing out on opportunities to share records we liked with our friends.</p>

			<h4 class="text-secondary">Our solution?</h4>
			<p>To address this problem, we built an app where you can <a href="/search/">search</a> for some music and find exactly what we love about it. We added tags to our favorite albums and you can use them to find more music with similar qualities.</p>
			<p>Not sure where to start? Check out our <a href="/favorites">favorite albums</a> of 2018 so far. Want to try some other features? Poke around using the 'Site Navigation' menu above, or look at the videos below showing some features of this app.</p>
